        @media screen {
            /*Lock and Denomination CSS*/
            .paper-wallet {

            }

            .lock-ctn {

                width: 120px;
                height: 103px;

                -webkit-transform-origin: top left;
                -webkit-transform: rotate(180deg);
                -moz-transform-origin: top left;
                -moz-transform: rotate(180deg);
                -ms-transform-origin: top left;
                -ms-transform: rotate(180deg);
                -o-transform-origin: top left;
                -o-transform: rotate(180deg);
                transform-origin: top left;
                transform: rotate(180deg);
            }

            .bip-encrypted {

                padding: 2px 0px;
                background-color: #000;
                color: #0d20fe;
                font-weight: 400;
                font-size: 9px;

                z-index: 100;
                position: absolute;
                width: 100%;

            .lock-art {

            .denomination {

                color: #0d20fe;
                font-weight: 400;
                letter-spacing: 2px;
                font-size: 22px;
                text-align: center;
                position: absolute;
                width: 100%;
                bottom: 0px;
                white-space: nowrap;
            }

            /* End Lock and Denomination CSS */
            /* Tooltip CSS */
            .tooltip {
                position: relative;
                display: inline-block;
                border-bottom: 1px dotted black;
                font-size: 0.55rem;
                vertical-align: middle;
            }

            .tooltip .tooltiptext {
                visibility: hidden;
                font-size: 1rem;
                width: 400px;
                background-color: #555;
                color: #fff;
                text-align: justify;
                border-radius: 6px;
                padding: 12px 12px;
                position: absolute;
                z-index: 1000;
                bottom: 125%;
                left: 50%;
                margin-left: -60px;
                opacity: 0;
                transition: opacity 0.3s;
            }

            .tooltip .tooltiptext::after {
                content: "";
                position: absolute;
                top: 100%;
                left: 50%;
                margin-left: -5px;
                border-width: 5px;
                border-style: solid;
                border-color: #555 transparent transparent transparent;
            }

            .tooltip:hover .tooltiptext {
                visibility: visible;
                opacity: 1;
            }

            /* End Tooltip CSS */
